{"tid":1387271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想share下做陪審員既經驗","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T20:07:59.000Z","uid":1025,"like":680,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"e6dfe570b7864267ccba88cfc1123ac3a96037e6","tid":1387271,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">痛心疾首</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/jury/jury_video.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fzh%2Fjury%2Fjury_video.html&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=ee1cb011\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/jury/jury_video.html</a><br />\n呢條係有關陪審員既短片有時間可以睇睇，但係畫面質素係咸豐年前<br />\n<br />\n入正題，出面好多post都有講點成為陪審員之類，但係好少人share經驗，如果有差希望法律手足幫手指正，我想補充係陪審員真係random，當中有指需要品格良好，所以大家盡量做個好市民，唔好俾人抄牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> p.s 希望有手足再補充何謂品格良好，eg泊車俾人炒左又仲係唔係<br />\n<br />\n1.好彩抽中<br />\n如果你被人挑選左做陪審員，你會收到一封通知書，如果你唔得閒你要係指定日子內解釋（好似係21日內），由你被挑選個刻開始，其實你直到上庭個日先知自己個日係審咩case，如果無記錯大家可以係上庭前一日check到個日咩庭有咩case<br />\n<br />\n2. 當日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/zh/jury/summoned_jurors_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fzh%2Fjury%2Fsummoned_jurors_tc.pdf&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=8c882461\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/zh/jury/summoned_jurors_tc.pdf</a> 你係需要早三日根據你sms或者email收到既code去登記出庭通知，之後佢會出庭前一日再confirm你出席，記得早少少去，去定個廁所，因為你報到後佢會再brief你一次，<span style=\"color: red;\">好啦重點來啦</span>，因為個日唔會淨係得一單案件，當日一行30－40人左右既陪審團會首次去左1號法庭（我當佢個日係有3個庭先），之後法官先會同你講呢單係咩case，然後就抽籤，佢有個箱仔，抽中你名你就要企出去中間，呢個時候控辯雙方<span style=\"color: red;\">會根據你個樣決定接唔接受你做陪審員</span>，係呀隨左你個名會被讀出，基本上真係睇你個樣，所以大家汁正d，（小弟當時係著恤衫西褲），之後你就會宣誓，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果個日係英文法官你就要英文宣誓</span>，誓詞有幾隻字好少見，記得查定點讀，有案例因為讀唔正／唔識讀而dq左個陪審，宣誓完後你就坐左係陪審席，直至夠數開座。<br />\n<br />\n而抽唔中既人會去2，3號庭重覆以上。如果都係抽唔中你你就可以番屋企<br />\n<br />\n3。開庭<br />\n你會收到好多由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />準備既文件，當中有份好似叫不可異議證供，入面所有野都係fact，法官會叫你一定要接受，咁呢度唔講太多了，到時你會識點做同法官會講之後點點點，最後就陪審團之間投票。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一定要盡公民責任，抽中就去做陪審員！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實和理非可以發揮既空間仲可以好大，d細路哥已經為左我地付出成世青春，佢地真係出番來都會收到一世既政治逼害，係我眼中香港好多和理非仲停留係嘴炮階段，我唔係叫你即時勇武，係你做得幾多得幾多，罷工既一齊罷，唔好辜負左一班年青人。政府係絕對絕對唔會放棄軍政府，我一諗起佢地俾班狗告暴動已經好想喊，盡力做好崗位，唔好放棄，香港有今時今日係因為我地都係世界仔用盡方法救自己。記住不分化不割蓆！<br />\n<br />\n天地有正氣，人賤自有天收"},{"pid":"07bbdac1c551e7a8bdeec6b71f0a4027674583af","tid":1387271,"uid":176102,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:32:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b20d99ea033a15f0b45751c0b044bc4a0520c60a","tid":1387271,"uid":72737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f6179edeaf9cec21608d2cb5af10d2a868bcae7","tid":1387271,"uid":18166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"076a5a33b36875f7612c1c59d087e8f0c3251ca0","tid":1387271,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"044ea1f99da8a21d21ce272591a2d1160cb1f8ba","tid":1387271,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"52355615c16e84e9dce951b2dfcc0d8e4d030a4e","tid":1387271,"uid":266181,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"I (name in full) swear by Almighty God that I will give a true verdict in this case according to the evidence.<br />\n天主教或基督教的宣誓誓詞英文版<br />\n<br />\nI (name) solemnly, sincerely, and truly declare and affirm that I will give a true verdict in this case according to the evidence.<br />\n非宗教式的宣誓誓詞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/64852/陪審員宣誓誓詞究竟點讀-英文達人蕭叔叔教你正確讀法\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F64852%2F%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E8%AA%93%E8%A9%9E%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E9%BB%9E%E8%AE%80-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA%E8%95%AD%E5%8F%94%E5%8F%94%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E8%AE%80%E6%B3%95&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=86108d9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/64852/陪審員宣誓誓詞究竟點讀-英文達人蕭叔叔教你正確讀法</a>"},{"pid":"f91bde5d76ef2f80c8cecec4ff52c6b623e20cd1","tid":1387271,"uid":1025,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"另外有人話會問你問題，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔 撚 會 問</span></span> ！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你個日只要乖乖地行陪審員通道，中間唔好同任何人接觸</span></span>就可以<br />\n<br />\n除左你識得被告要申報外"},{"pid":"ed118b29501b3cecfe2f6c5aef53dc07d3b8935a","tid":1387271,"uid":51641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"前線唔係condom!"},{"pid":"7d9ce6a5da46f26921430cde8f79db4048d7f933","tid":1387271,"uid":215769,"like":0,"dislike":61,"