ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"有無高院法庭書記巴絲分享下?"},{"pid":"404522ae31fe20770d4f28e1b9cd16f4b03dd0ae","tid":1387271,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9858e3836f33b11491e5d821e3a3a7a3f6779d7","tid":1387271,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"退庭商議果陣係點？小組討論？唔出聲又點？投票果陣又係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"詳情我唔知講唔講得 不過可以quote番佢官網 同埋全程係聽多過講野<br />\n<br />\n陪審員的職責<br />\n<br />\n在刑事案件審訊中，陪審員須根據案件中的事實，決定案中的被告人是否有罪。在死因研訊中，陪審員則須決定死者的致死原因及與死亡事件有關的情況。<br />\n<br />\n審訊時，主審法官會決定陪審團可聆聽甚麼證供，然而在陪審團考慮裁決時，則由陪審團自行決定有關證供的重要性。 ＜法官會用佢法律官點提醒你證供可信性同重要性<br />\n<br />\n陪審團商議的內容須絕對保密。陪審員務須小心，切勿與陪審團成員以外的任何人士談論案件。"},{"pid":"cd26179a83d8e08b34874f60986546b9b959506d","tid":1387271,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"becc75094f37bef8d7922009dae4cc12e4fa6443","tid":1387271,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efd1d0dd6a688ac4fbc662064cdceb6c2f3ff393","tid":1387271,"uid":266433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db49ddc09527547b5d9f0831ddd3bf8756c6f0ca","tid":1387271,"uid":43141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4NYrP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4NYrP4.jpg&h=23d94e3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"控辯兩方都可以reject架，幾多次唔記得，但一定有限制。"},{"pid":"ff1ec6675abf1062d2026fb72bcbea24aeddf93c","tid":1387271,"uid":1025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fafee3c6934b3532b0c5869b4e96df2af7b5800e","tid":1387271,"uid":145062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6990afa3c58e30b3390073b53ea204e7ee28eb0","tid":1387271,"uid":18